---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy — IMTI" description="Cookie Policy for India Market Timing Index">
  <div class="card" style="max-width:800px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:16px;">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:24px;">Last updated: April 23, 2026</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help us provide and improve our services.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
    <table style="margin:12px 0;">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Type</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Essential</strong></td>
          <td>Site functionality, authentication, security</td>
          <td>Session / 1 year</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Analytics</strong></td>
          <td>Google Analytics — anonymized usage stats</td>
          <td>2 years</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Advertising</strong></td>
          <td>Google AdSense — personalized ads (with consent)</td>
          <td>1 year</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Preferences</strong></td>
          <td>Remember your settings (theme, consent choices)</td>
          <td>1 year</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use services from the following providers that may set cookies:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left:20px;color:var(--text-secondary);">
      <li><strong>Google:</strong> Analytics, AdSense, reCAPTCHA, Firebase Auth</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> CDN and security</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p>You can manage or delete cookies through your browser settings. You can also update your consent preferences using the cookie banner at the bottom of the page.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">5. Contact</h2>
    <p>For cookie-related queries, email <a href="mailto:support@imti.in">support@imti.in</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
